snippet.title: Trivia Tricks - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Trivia Tricks is a trivia party game played online and locally with up to 8 players! Flex your brain muscle across a wide range of categories and see who will come out on top!

Wishlist on Steam ahead of the release on October 27th!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1404090/Trivia_Tricks

Follow us on twitter: www.twitter.com/triviatricks
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/sUwKvCb
